description: Creates a shipping label that will be used to return the Snow device to Amazon Web Services.

parameters.name: JobId
parameters.description: The ID for a job that you want to create the return shipping label for; for example, JID123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status information of the task on a Snow device that is being returned to Amazon Web Services.
